videos.description: Xavier Rathan-Mayes sends a lob up to Michael Ojo for a two-handed jam early in the first half against Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (FSU's Ojo throws down two-handed jam) 2017/1/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU's Ojo throws down two-handed jam

videos.description: 1H (6:27) FSU Terance Mann made Dunk. Assisted by Dwayne Bacon.
videos.headline: T. Mann made Dunk. Assisted by D. Bacon.

videos.description: Grayson Allen drives the lane, makes a tough layup and draws a foul in the final minutes of the first half against Florida State.
videos.headline: Allen hits tough layup and draws a foul

videos.description: Florida State's Michael Ojo throws it down baseline early in the second half against Duke.
videos.headline: Ojo hammers it home for FSU

videos.description: 2H (13:27) FSU Jarquez Smith made Dunk. Assisted by Braian Angola-Rodas.
videos.headline: J. Smith made Dunk. Assisted by B. Angola-Rodas.

videos.description: Jonathan Isaac throws down a powerful alley-oop from Xavier Rathan-Mayes in the second half to give Florida State a four-point lead over Duke.
videos.headline: FSU's Isaac finishes huge alley-oop over Duke

videos.description: Florida State's Jonathan Isaac comes up with a huge blocked shot at the rim, denying Duke's Jayson Tatum with less than five minutes on the clock.
videos.headline: Isaac denies Duke at the rim

videos.description: Jarquez Smith and Jonathan Isaac team up for a powerful alley-oop in the final minute of the game to seal Florida State's win over Duke and the Seminoles remain undefeated in the ACC.
videos.headline: FSU remains unbeaten in ACC as huge alley-oop seals victory over Duke

videos.description: Seth Greenberg says Duke misses Amile Jefferson while he's out with an injury and likens his tendency to be in the right place to Clemson linebacker Ben Boulware.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Greenberg: Amile Jefferson is Duke's Ben Boulware) 2017/01/10 SC

videos.headline: Greenberg: Amile Jefferson is Duke's Ben Boulware
